author: Larry Brown
title: Week 5 expert NFL Picks against the spread – Doc’s locks
text:
0 0 
Doc Brown had a miserable Week 4 in the picks. Just about everything except the lock went wrong. When he picked favorites, they lost. When he went dogs, they got blown out. It just didn’t work out. But for every negative, there’s a positive, and that means this should be a bounce-back week for the Doc.
